%h2 Nested Grids

%p Grids also support nested grids, such as:

%pre
  %code
    :preserve
      &lt;div class="grid"&gt;
        &lt;div class="grid-col grid-3-5"&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="grid-col grid-2-5"&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="grid-col grid-2-10"&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="grid-col grid-8-10"&gt;
          &lt;div class="grid"&gt;
            &lt;div class="grid-col grid-2-4"&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class="grid-col grid-1-4"&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class="grid-col grid-1-4"&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="grid-col grid-4-12&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="grid-col grid-8-12&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;

